{"title":"火的喷泉——石景山诗草","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的喷泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——石景山诗草\t顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的喷泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写于转钢炉边）一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根火柱冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一簇簇火花飞溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我在这里看到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个火的喷泉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠泉虽然美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趵突泉可算奇观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是怎能比得上火的喷泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样使人雀跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人心欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的喷泉震响祖国的豪语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的喷泉传出幸福的呢喃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷泉喷出灿烂的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷泉喷出永不消逝的春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷人的图画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔写于高炉旁〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍名山大川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看尽珍草奇花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但最最使我爱慕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是这一座座铁塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔顶云烟缭绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔下铁水喧哗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤褐色的矿石堆成山岳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一幅迷人的图画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让这图画布满祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让这图画到处悬挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这崭新的景色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要代替古庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻名天下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐的回声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人眺望京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有各种不同兴奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人望着琉璃瓦发呆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人望着红旗出神……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们炼钢炼铁的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜爱看浓烟上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走遍京城的街道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都听到欢乐的回声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下回旋着多少钢管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是我们的双手铸成；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空飞驰着多少神鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机舱里也有我们的劳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人眺望京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有各种不同兴奋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在熔炉旁挥汗的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪迈的激情更沸腾！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}